{"tid":2284262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蠶食美國｜強烈推薦這兩集記錄片，談到socialism/communism 在美國的滲透","createTime":"2020-11-13T07:08:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T08:13:47.000Z","uid":294518,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"564d51dc0dc6f30a336fd79d423867aeff624baa","tid":2284262,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T07:08:19.000Z","msg":"蠶食美國｜強烈推薦這兩集記錄片，談到socialism/communism 在美國的滲透。<br />\n<br />\n1.https://<a href=\"http://m.youtube.com/watch?v=Hk_4HOz5za0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHk_4HOz5za0&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOIg5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=5c93150d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">m.youtube.com/watch?v=Hk_4HOz5za0</a> <br />\n<br />\n2.https://<a href=\"http://m.youtube.com/watch?v=tTltPFeYex0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtTltPFeYex0&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOIg5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=cf094b6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">m.youtube.com/watch?v=tTltPFeYex0</a><br />\n<br />\n由前Idaho州議員Curtis Bowers(9個孩子的父親，基督徒）導演的兩集記錄片Agenda（中文翻譯為「蠶食美國」）。本記錄片採訪了許多知名學者，從政治，經濟，宗教，教育，環保，媒體等方面詳細記載暴露了socialism/communism 在美國的侵蝕與滲透以及如何改變美國文化，特別是下一代的教育思想理念。<br />\n<br />\n影片曾獲2010 San Antonio Independent Christian Film 的大獎。這是2010年製作完成，今年2020 年來看這影片，只能越來越看到影片的預見性。"},{"pid":"6e1f35e089b2a0464273eed840d9697a2374f0c1","tid":2284262,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T07:10:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e054fbc7ef2339e472b7796fa88fcd6ae1eb263a","tid":2284262,"uid":308915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T08:11:27.000Z","msg":"決定由今日開始一見到左膠就屌鳩佢racist屌到佢地懷疑人生<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2284071\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2284071</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"99bdc96ed715c0c7f28d97ad690b811d546c3463","tid":2284262,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T08:13:47.000Z","